OL,3,CMore than 200 pubs closed in six
OL,4,Cmonths amid tax hikes, figures show
OL,6,FEight pubs a week shut their doors for
OL,7,Fgood across the UK over the first half
OL,8,Fof the year amid rising tax and labour
OL,9,Fcosts, according to new figures.
OL,11,FIndustry bosses said it is
OL,12,F"heartbreaking" and highlighted the
OL,13,Fneed for supportive tax measures from
OL,14,Fthe Treasury in the autumn budget.
OL,16,FOfficial Government statistics show
OL,17,F209 pubs were demolished or converted
OL,18,Ffor other uses over the six months to
OL,19,FJune.
