OL,3,CMore than 200 pubs closed in six
OL,4,Cmonths amid tax hikes, figures show
OL,6,FThe data, which was analysed by
OL,7,Fcommercial real estate specialists at
OL,8,FRyan, show the overall number of pubs
OL,9,Fin England and Wales, including those
OL,10,Fvacant and being offered to let, fell
OL,11,Fto 38,780.
OL,13,FIt means 2,283 pubs have vanished from
OL,14,Fcommunities across England and Wales
OL,15,Fforever since the start of 2020.
OL,17,FValuation Office Agency data shows
OL,18,Fmany of these have been demolished or
OL,19,Fconverted into homes, offices or other
OL,20,Fuses such as day nurseries.
