OL,3,CMore than 200 pubs closed in six
OL,4,Cmonths amid tax hikes, figures show
OL,6,FThe South East was hit hardest in the
OL,7,Ffirst half of 2025, losing 31 pubs in
OL,8,Fjust six months, according to the data.
OL,10,FThe closures come amid an intensifying
OL,11,Fbackdrop for UK pubs, which were
OL,12,Fimpacted by increases to the national
OL,13,Fminimum wage, national insurance
OL,14,Fpayments and business rates payments.
OL,16,FIn April, the national living wage
OL,17,Frose by 6.7% to #12.21 an hour for
OL,18,Fworkers aged 21 and older.
