OL,3,CMore than 200 pubs closed in six
OL,4,Cmonths amid tax hikes, figures show
OL,6,FIndustry bosses had warned the jump in
OL,7,Ftaxes particularly would lead to an
OL,8,Facceleration in pub closures.
OL,10,FEmma McClarkin, chief executive of the
OL,11,FBritish Beer and Pub Association, said
OL,12,Fthe Government needs to act quickly to
OL,13,Fsave pubs across the country.
OL,15,FShe said: "It's absolutely
OL,16,Fheartbreaking and there is a direct
OL,17,Flink between pubs closing for good and
OL,18,Fthe huge jump in costs they have just
OL,19,Fendured.
