OL,3,CMore than 200 pubs closed in six
OL,4,Cmonths amid tax hikes, figures show
OL,6,FAlex Probyn, practice leader of
OL,7,Fproperty tax at Ryan, warned the
OL,8,Fsqueeze on the pub trade is
OL,9,Fintensifying.
OL,11,FHe said: "Slashing business rates
OL,12,Frelief for pubs from 75% to 40% this
OL,13,Fyear has landed the sector with an
OL,14,Fextra #215 million in tax bills.
OL,16,F"For a small pub, that's a leap in the
OL,17,Faverage bill from #3,938 to #9,451 ` a
OL,18,F140% increase.
